Direct Known Subclasses:
CssPanelController, DocumentPanelController, DummyWindowController, ImageLibraryPanelController, InspectorPanelController, LibraryPanelController, LogViewerController, SkeletonWindowController, SourceViewWindowController
public abstract class AbstractFxmlViewController
extends AbstractFxmlController
implements View, ViewContent, ViewMenuProvider
AbstractViewFxmlPanelController is the abstract base class for all the view controller which build their UI components from an FXML file. Subclasses should provide a AbstractFxmlController.controllerDidLoadFxml() method in charge of finishing the initialization of the UI components loaded from the FXML file. It provides input controls for filtering, a placeholder menu and basic docking functionalities
